{{Infobox Convention |name = International Defence Exhibition (IDEX) |logo = IDEX 2011 Logo.png |logo_size=162px |logo_caption = IDEX 2011 logo |genre = Defense |venue = Abu Dhabi National Exhibition Centre |location = [[Abu Dhabi]] |country = United Arab Emirates |first = 1993 |last = |organized = ADNEC in coordination with the UAE Armed Forces GHQ |attendance = Nearly 45,000 in 2009 |website = [http://www.idexuae.ae www.idexuae.ae] }}
The '''International Defence Exhibition & Conference''', or '''IDEX''', is a biennial arms and defence technology sales exhibition. According to the [[Jane's Defence Weekly]] website, IDEX is the largest arms exhibition in the [[Middle East]]. The business conducted at the 2005 IDEX totalled 2 billion US dollars. According to [[Stockholm International Peace Research Institute]], the arms sales of the SIPRI Top 100 arms-producing and military services companies in 2013 (outside China) totalled 402 billion US dollars.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sipri.org/media/pressreleases/2014/SIPRI-Top-100-December-2014|title=Sales by largest arms companies fell again in 2013 but Russian firms’ sales continued rising - SIPRI|website=www.sipri.org}}</ref>
IDEX for the past several show have been held in the [[United Arab Emirates]] (U.A.E.) at [[Abu Dhabi]] and will again host in 2015. Sheikh [[Khalifa Bin Zayed Al Nahyan]], President of the UAE and Supreme Commander of the UAE Armed Forces is the show's benefactor. It was previously held at the [[Abu Dhabi National Exhibition Centre]] and will be held at the same place again in 2015.
As of 2010 well known exhibitors for the 2011 show are [[Lockheed Martin]], [[Airbus|Airbus Group]], Jobaria Defence, Streit Group, [[Oshkosh Corporation]] and [[Saab Group|Saab]]. The show is organized through the state-run Abu Dhabi National Exhibitions Company ([[ADNEC]]), managed by [[Humaid Matar Al Dhaheri]].
==See also== * [[IMDEX]]—the International Maritime Defence Exhibition * [[International Defence Industry Fair|IDEF]]—Defence expo in [[Istanbul]], [[Turkey]] * [[DefExpo]]—Defence expo in [[New Delhi]], [[India]] * [[DIMDEX]]—Defence expo in [[Doha]], [[Qatar]] * [[International Defence Exhibition and Seminar|IDEAS]]—Defence expo in [[Karachi]], [[Pakistan]] * [[Special Operations Forces Exhibition| Special Operations Forces Exhibition (SOFEX)]]—Defence expo in [[Amman]], [[Jordan]] * [[Eurosatory]]—Defence expo in [[Paris]], [[France]] * [[MSPO]]—Defence expo in [[Kielce]], [[Poland]] * [[CMME]]-Civil-Military Technology Equipment Expo in [[Beijing]], [[China]]
