'''Thomas Allan Napier Corson''' (25 February 1902&ndash;30 April 1972) was a New Zealand businessman and local politician. He was born in [[Napier, New Zealand|Napier]], [[Hawke's Bay]], [[New Zealand]] on 25 February 1902.<ref name="DNZB Corson">{{DNZB|title=Thomas Allan Napier Corson|first= Iain|last= Gillies|id=5c36|accessdate=30 December 2016}}</ref>

